{
  "chapter": 24,
  "chapter_summary": "李寻欢与心树推断心眉大师身中两种毒——极乐童子的\"五毒水晶\"与另一种阴毒之药，后者毒性克制前者，才使遗体未生异变。由此锁定配药的七师弟心宠（俗名单鹗，出家前人称\"七巧书生\"）为盗经杀人真凶。心湖大师院中，心树当众揭发心宠，心宠矢口否认。李寻欢设下圈套，令心宠在搜查易筋经时不打自招。此时百晓生突然发难，扣住心湖大师要挟众人。李寻欢飞刀出手，百晓生咽喉中刀倒下。混乱中心宠逃窜，欲杀阿飞泄愤，却被阿飞以一根冰柱刺穿咽喉毙命。李寻欢与阿飞辞别少林，路上讨论梅花盗身份，李寻欢提出梅花盗或许并非男子而是女子。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "你的运气不错，被他毒死的人实在不好看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "多年前，我曾经看到过一个被他毒死的人，那人中毒才不过片刻，全身已经发黑，我出去打个转，再回去一看，那人身上的肉已全都不见了，已变成了一副骷髅——漆黑的骷髅！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但现在二师兄中毒已有好几天了……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "不错，他中毒已有数日，却还没有发生那种可怕的变化，你可知道是为了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "这只因他又中了另外一种极厉害的毒！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你……你是说……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "他虽中了极乐童子的'五毒水晶'，但中的毒并不深，再被他以内力逼住，所以他直到回来后毒性还未发作。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "正是如此。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "那凶手为了怕他说出秘密，一心想他快些死，生怕他中的毒还不够深，就另给他服了一种极厉害的毒药。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "杀人的法子很多，他为什么还是要用毒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "只因无论用什么法子杀人，都难免留下痕迹，大家既已都知道心眉大师中了毒，他只有再用下毒这法子，才能避免别人的疑心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "不错，这样做人人都认定二师兄必是被极乐童子毒死的，再也不会怀疑到他身上了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "此人行事，虽然老谋深算，只可惜还是忘了一件事。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "他忘了毒性必相克，就因为他们下的毒既烈又重，克住了'五毒水晶'之毒，所以心眉大师的遗蜕到现在还未有那种可怕的变化！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你的意思我明白了，只不过那下毒的人是谁，你我还是不知道。",
      "tone": "沉思",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "心眉大师回来之后，可曾服用过什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "只吃过一碗药。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "是谁喂他吃药的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "药是七师弟心宠配的，但喂他吃药的人，却是四师兄心烛和六师弟心灯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "所以这三个人都有下毒的机会。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "世上的毒药大致可分为两类，第一类毒药虽然五色无味，但却可令中毒的人死得很惨，叫别人看了害怕，只因这类毒不但要取人性命，还有要向人示威之意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "那'五毒水晶'自然是属于这一类的毒药了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "第二类毒，也许并非无色无味，但却可令被毒死的人死后全无异状，甚至叫别人看不出他是被毒死的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你说那凶手就是用的这种毒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "就因为两种毒性迥异，是以才会互相克制，那第一类毒虽可怕，这第二类毒却更阴毒，江湖中能用这类毒的人并不多。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "少林门下，善于用毒的人有几个？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "少林寺领袖江湖，武林正宗，少林弟子也以此为荣，绝不会有人肯去学这种下五门的手段，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "少林七十二绝艺中，绝没有这'毒'字！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "心烛大师和心灯大师……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "四师兄九岁时便已落发，六师弟更在襁褓中便已入了佛门，他两人这一生中只怕还未见过毒药！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "如此说来，下毒的人是谁呢？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你难道说的是七师弟心宠？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看……李寻欢会不会出来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xiao_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "百晓生",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "毫无疑问。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_bai_xiao_sheng",
      "text": "他这种人难道还为会了朋友而牺牲自己？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xiao_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "百晓生",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "这就叫'盗亦有道'。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但愿如此……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "你可安好？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "多谢师兄关切，弟子侥幸逃过了这一劫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "心宠",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "李寻欢呢？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_xin_chong",
      "text": "他取经去了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "心宠",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "取经？取什么经？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_xin_chong",
      "text": "艺经阁内失窃的经。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "心宠",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "盗经的人果然是他！师兄你怎地放心让他去？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_xin_chong",
      "text": "只因盗经的人并不是他！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_xin_chong",
      "text": "盗经的人就是谋害二师兄的凶手，因为二师兄已发现了这人的秘密，他只有将二师兄杀死灭口，但这人却并非李寻欢！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "心宠",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "不是李寻欢是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_xin_chong",
      "text": "是你！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "心宠",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "五师兄怎会说出这种话来，我倒真有些不懂了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_xin_chong",
      "text": "你不懂还有谁懂？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "心宠",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "这件事还是请大师兄裁夺，弟子无话可说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "二师弟明明是遭了李寻欢之毒手，你为何要为他洗脱？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xiao_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "百晓生",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "若是在下记得不错，心树师兄与李寻欢好像还是同榜的进土。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "心宠",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "五师兄只怕也中了李寻欢的毒了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_xin_chong",
      "text": "真正令二师兄致命的毒药，并非极乐童子的'五毒水晶'……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "心宠",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "师兄你又怎会知道的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_xin_chong",
      "text": "你以为你做的事真的人不知，鬼不觉？\n\n你莫非已忘了二师兄临死前还有这本东西留下来？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "这又是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "二师兄临行之前，已发现了那盗经的叛徒，只是他心存仁厚，未经证实前，还不愿披露这叛徒的姓名，只不过却已将之写在他这本'读经鎏记'上，以防万一他若有不测，也好留作证据。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "真有此事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "心宠",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "这上面若真有我的名字，我就甘愿……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_xin_chong",
      "text": "你甘愿怎样？……你虽已将最后一页撕下了，又怎知二师兄就没有记在另一页上？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "心宠",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "五师兄竟勾结外人，令弟子身遭不白之冤，求大师兄明辨。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xiao_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "百晓生",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "白纸上写的虽是黑字，但这字却是人人都可写的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "心宠",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "不错，就算二师兄这本'读经鎏记'上写着我的名字，但却也未必是二师兄自己写的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xiao_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "百晓生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "据我所知，小李探花文武双全，韩苏颜柳，兰庭魏碑，名家的字，他却曾下过功夫临摹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "心宠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，他若要学一个人的笔迹，自然容易得很。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "你平时素来谨慎，这次怎地也疏忽起来？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "师兄若认为这证据不够，还有个证据。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "你且说出来。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "本来藏在二师兄房中的那部'达摩易筋经'，也已失窃了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "李探花算准这部经必定还未及送走，必定还藏在心宠房里，是以弟子已令值日的一尘和一茵监视着他一起取经去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "心宠",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "师兄切莫听他的，他倒真是想栽赃！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_chong",
      "text": "就算我们是栽赃，但你又怎知我们会将这部经放在这木柜里？\n你为何不到别处去找？一进来就直奔这木柜？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "李探花早已算准只有用这法子，才可令他不打自招的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我这法子实在也用得很冒险，他自己若不上当，那就谁也无法令他招认了！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_chong",
      "text": "单鹗，少林待你不薄，你为何今日做出这种事来？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "单鹗",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "弟子……弟子知错了。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "单鹗",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "但弟子也是受了他人指使，被他人所诱，才会一时糊涂。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_chong",
      "text": "你受了谁的指使？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xiao_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "百晓生",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "指使他的人，我倒可猜出一二。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_bai_xiao_sheng",
      "text": "先生指教。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xiao_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "百晓生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就是他！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_bai_xiao_sheng",
      "text": "指使他的人原来是你！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xiao_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "百晓生",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "在下只不过想借贵寺的藏经一阅而已，谁知道各位竟如此小气？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_bai_xiao_sheng",
      "text": "我与你数十年相交，不想你竟如此待我？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xiao_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "百晓生",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "我本来也不想如此对你的，怎奈单鹗定要拖我下水，我若不出手救他，他怎会放过我？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_bai_xiao_sheng",
      "text": "只可惜谁也救不了他了！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chong",
      "speaker_name": "单鹗",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "不错，谁也救不了我，只有你才救得了我，现在我就要你送我们下山……你们若还要你们的掌门人活着，最好谁也莫要妄动！",
      "tone": "狞笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_chong",
      "text": "你们若以少林为重，就莫要管我！还不动手拿下这叛徒！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xiao_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "百晓生",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "你无论怎么说，他们也不会拿你的性命来开玩笑的，少林派掌门人的一条命比别人一千条命还要值钱得多。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "百晓生作兵器谱，口评天下兵器，可称武林智者，谁知到头来还是难免死在自己所品评的兵器之下。",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老僧也错了。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那叛徒呢？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "两位请到老僧……",
      "tone": "谦恭",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "李寻欢是不是梅花盗？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "我是不是梅花盗？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "檀越也不是。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "既然不是，我们可以走了么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "自然可以，只不过檀越……檀越行动似还有些不便，不如先请到……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "这不用你费心，莫说我还可以走。\n\n就算爬，也要爬下山去！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "今日就此别过，他日或当再见，大师请恕我等无礼。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我送你们一程。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_shu",
      "text": "送即不送，不送即送，大师何必客气？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_shu",
      "speaker_name": "心树",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "既然送即不送，送又何妨，檀越又何必客气？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "心烛",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "师兄也许不该让他们走的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_zhu",
      "text": "为何不该？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "心烛",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "李寻欢虽未盗经，也不是杀死二师兄的凶手，但这还是不能证明他并非梅花盗！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_zhu",
      "text": "你要怎样证明？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "心烛",
      "listener": "char_xin_hu",
      "text": "除非他能将那真的梅花盗找出来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_hu",
      "speaker_name": "心湖大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_zhu",
      "text": "我想他一定会找出来的，而且一定会送到这里，这都用不着我们关心，只有那六部经……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你说你不是梅花盗，我也不是，那么梅花盗是谁呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "梅花盗已死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "他真的死了？你杀死的那人真是梅花盗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "不知你有没有想到过，梅花盗也许不是男人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "不是男人是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "不是男人自然是女人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    }
  ],
  "new_entities": {
    "characters": [
      {
        "id": "char_xin_chong",
        "name": "心宠",
